---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import backgroundColour from "../images/bg.webp";
---

<Layout>
    <section class="relative min-h-screen">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
                <article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert mx-auto">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                        Professional Web Design & Development Services by Uys Design
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl text-blue-400 mb-8">Custom Code – No Page Builders or WordPress</h2>

                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
                        At Uys Design, we take a unique approach to web design. Unlike others who rely on page builders or WordPress, we hand-code every website from scratch. This ensures:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="text-gray-300 mb-12 list-none pl-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Fully Custom Designs: Tailored to your brand and goals.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Zero Bloat: No wasted code, so your site loads instantly.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Perfect Google Page Speed Scores: Achieve top marks on Core Web Vitals.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Unmatched Security: No databases or plugins to exploit, making our sites virtually unhackable.</li>
                        <li>✓ No Maintenance Hassles: Forget constant updates or plugin management.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-4">Why It Matters</h3>
                    <ul class="text-gray-300 mb-12 list-none pl-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Faster Load Times: Capture more leads by keeping visitors engaged.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Higher Conversions: Better ad performance and lower bounce rates.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Improved Google Rankings: Dominate search results with faster, optimized sites.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Enhanced Security: Protect your business with hack-proof websites.</li>
                        <li>✓ Boosted Google Business Profile: Increase visibility in local searches.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-4">Faster Load Times = Higher Conversions</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
                        In today's competitive online landscape, every second counts. If your website takes more than 3 seconds to load, you could lose up to 50% of your visitors. At Uys Design, we create custom-coded websites that load instantly, ensuring your audience stays engaged and converts into leads.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-4">Small Business SEO Specialists</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
                        At Uys Design, we know that web design and SEO go hand in hand. Our in-house SEO expert, Cobus Uys, specializes in:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="text-gray-300 mb-12 list-none pl-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Content Creation: Crafting helpful, engaging content that ranks.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">✓ Backlink Strategies: Building authority through high-quality links.</li>
                        <li>✓ Ongoing Monitoring: Continuously optimizing your site for better results.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-12">
                        Forget the basics like meta tags and sitemaps—those are standard. Real SEO is an active process, and we're here to guide you every step of the way.
                    </p>

                    <div class="text-center mt-16 mb-8">
                        <p class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-8">
                            Ready to Transform Your Online Presence?
                        </p>
                        <a 
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-md transition duration-300"
                        >
                            Contact Us Today
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>